setSpaceships(List<Spaceship>) - Method in class aoop.asteroids.model.game.ServerGame
Replaces this game's spaceships with the new list of spaceships,
Afterwards, these are all reset (set to 'alive') and positioned at the center of the screen.
Used when starting a new game round.
-> In singleplayer mode, the single ship is rendered in the middle of the screen, pointing up.
-> In multiplayer, ships are set in a circle, pointing outward.

SpectatorPingPacket - Class in aoop.asteroids.udp.packets
Sent by the Spectator every few milliseconds, to let the Server know that the Spectator is still listening to the connection, and watching the game.
Does not contain actual data, as only the timestamp of the Packet is needed in this case.
